title: Fujitsu SC2: Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/server/fujitsu
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors different temperature sensors
 on Fujitsu Siemens Servers which support the
 FSC-SERVERCONTROL2-MIB.

 The check goes WARN or CRIT if the
 power consumption is higher or lower than the
 configurable levels or if it exceeds critical
 levels defined on the device.

item:
 The temperature sensor designation

inventory:
 One service per sensor is created.

